{"tid":819753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(Hehe) 中意左自己呀哥，應該點做?","createTime":"2018-09-15T05:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T00:24:00.000Z","uid":181662,"like":37,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"094eb17ddcaeac60cc2d5f37fcb22ba05a42a987","tid":819753,"uid":181662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"我小學二年級個陣老母再婚<br />\n嫁左俾而家既老豆<br />\n而家個老豆本身又有個仔<br />\n姐係我有個無血緣既呀哥<br />\n<br />\n呀哥今年form 6，我細佢5年<br />\n佢一直當我親細佬咁照顧<br />\n我又一直好中意佢<br />\n<br />\n但最近我開始對佢有ff<br />\n仲偷偷地拿佢著完既底褲黎打J<br />\n仲會搵一d兄弟相姦既GV黎睇<br />\n我開始ff同呀哥做愛， 佢攻我受<br />\n<br />\n我呀哥係學校都算係校草<br />\n但到而家佢都無拍過拖<br />\n佢d fd多數都係男仔<br />\n<br />\n係屋企既時候，<br />\n佢好多時會攬住我，<br />\n有時會一齊訓到天光<br />\n<br />\n前幾日係佢訓左既時候，<br />\n我偷摸佢條J, <br />\n摸到佢硬晒佢都冇醒<br />\n<br />\n我其實好想含佢，<br />\n但又怕佢發覺左唔知會點，<br />\n究竟我應唔應該咁做?"},{"pid":"aa5af8e69091e2a6a4f2a6d14e9c323247a66f1d","tid":819753,"uid":68081,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"買朱古力，之後大家自然會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce7abcbb559afb7887426025e7adc6f541c3541","tid":819753,"uid":208516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"bf4224291359896bca3a9c0c8db858b218eb5675","tid":819753,"uid":181662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5af8e69091e2a6a4f2a6d14e9c323247a66f1d","tid":819753,"uid":68081,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"買朱古力，之後大家自然會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"買朱古力?<br />\n其實我想知佢係咪hehe"},{"pid":"f6b88139c833f3d694921